This level is possible

--Intended with all Characters--

Vanquish the Palace of the Koopas as you dodge vicious traps and tricks!

--Significantly harder as Luigi--
Rattle me bones! the big boo's new fortress is filled with bones and boos! think you can find the special treasure and take down the boss?

Solve puzzles, fill in empty spaces, set record time .. and play sudoku. Except it isn't sudoku? I'm baffled at what it's called. 

Hint: Make sure not to have a starman while getting a goomba's shoe.

Ultra Star-esque Fast Parabeetle Platforming.
NOTE FOR SECTION 2: You can walk off a ledge and jump in midair with the kuribo's shoe.
Bullets everywhere, and they're all dangerous! either they'll turn back to try to hit you again, or just seek you down for the perfect shot!

Guide your way through this tough world with your skills and expertise! This world will train your ability to.. do stuff?
--Use with Mario, Luigi is pretty hard to complete--
A nasty short showcasing the unpredictability of chain chomps.  see if you make make it through!
Mario wakes up late because his youtube channel left him 5 years ago, you will have less than 8 seconds to run quite fast, put it to the test
